description: Disney's live-action 'Snow White' opened to a disappointing $43 million at the box office despite a $250 million budget. The film faced controversies over CGI dwarfs and comments by star Rachel Zegler, alongside poor reviews. Globally, it earned $87.3 million, falling short of expectations, raising questions about Disney's strategy for future live-action remakes.
title: 'Snow White' underperforms with $87.3 million opening weekend collection

description: Habitat Studio in Mumbai has announced its temporary closure after Shiv Sena workers vandalized the venue over a jibe by comedian Kunal Kamra at Deputy Chief Minister Eknath Shinde. An FIR has been registered against those responsible for the vandalism. Kamra had made the remarks during a stand-up performance.
title: 'Shutting down': Kunal Kamra’s show organisers react to Shiv Sena vandalism

description: Sudha Murty reflects on the hard work and sacrifices that built Infosys, discussing her husband Narayana Murthy's controversial suggestion of working 70 hours a week. She highlights their mutual support, balancing her husband's dedication to the company with her commitment to family.
title: Sudha Murty talks about Narayana Murthy's '70-hr work week': There was no...
Watch: Elon Musk's balancing act goes viral, literally!

description: The CBI has closed the investigation into Sushant Singh Rajput’s death and ruled out foul play, bringing relief to Rhea and Showik Chakraborty. Celebrities are now calling for apologies to the Chakraborty family for the media harassment they endured.
title: Dia Mirza demands apology for Rhea Chakraborty after CBI rules out foul play in Sushant Rajput case

description: Harbhajan Singh made a controversial comment comparing Jofra Archer to a 'black taxi' during an IPL 2025 match, causing backlash on social media. Archer had a forgetful record-breaking expensive performance, conceding 76 runs without a wicket against Sunrisers Hyderabad on Sunday. Sunrisers Hyderabad posted 286 in the fixture
title: Harbhajan in racism row after comments towards Archer

description: In the IPL clash between Chennai Super Kings and Mumbai Indians, debutant Vignesh Puthur, a 24-year-old chinaman bowler from Kerala, impressed with 3/32. Puthur, picked up at the auction for Rs 30 lakh, was praised for his accuracy, cool head under pressure, and quick adaptation to the high-level game.
title: How MI scouted, groomed Vignesh Puthur for the big IPL stage

description: Israel's military struck the Nasser Hospital in Gaza, targeting a senior Hamas operative. The attack, which resulted in casualties and a fire, comes amid renewed Israeli offensives. More than 50,000 Palestinians have died in the ongoing conflict. Political tensions escalate in Israel, where public frustration grows against Prime Minister Netanyahu, while Gaza's humanitarian crisis worsens.
title: Israel bombs largest hospital in southern Gaza; top Hamas official killed

description: Comedian Kunal Kamra sparked controversy by calling Maharashtra deputy CM Eknath Shinde a 'gaddar' during a Mumbai show. Shiv Sena workers vandalized the venue, and an FIR was filed against Kamra. Shiv Sena leaders demanded his apology within two days, while opposition leaders defended Kamra and condemned the attack as cowardice.
title: Kamra vs Sena: Joke on Shinde triggers major row; venue vandalised, FIR filed

description: Eyewitnesses recounted the terror in Jammu & Kashmir's Kathua, where a gunfight erupted between security forces and heavily armed terrorists. Anita Devi narrowly escaped after terrorists held her husband at gunpoint. Intense gunfire ensued, with around '250 rounds' heard. The operation was based on intelligence indicating terrorist presence near the Pakistan border.
title: 'Husband held at gunpoint': Civilian recounts encounter with terrorists in J&K

description: Salman Khan's recent appearance in a clean-shaven look caused fans to worry about his health and age. The actor clarified that his tired appearance was due to sleep deprivation and long shooting hours for his film 'Sikandar'. He also addressed concerns about the age gap with his co-star, Rashmika Mandanna.
title: 'Still have it in me': Salman Khan reacts to his viral clean shaven pics

description: Stock market recommendations: Motilal Oswal Financial Services Ltd recommends Amber Enterprises and Kirloskar Oil for the week. Amber's revenue grew by 65% YoY in Q3FY25, driven by RAC and electronics. Kirloskar Oil is expected to benefit from stable demand in powergen segments.
title: Stock recommendations for the week starting March 24

description: Brady Tkachuk, captain of the Ottawa Senators, shared insights on how the intense 4 Nations Face-Off tournament, where he played with his brother Matthew for Team USA, shaped his competitive spirit for the NHL playoffs. Tkachuk aims to bring the same high-stakes mindset to guide the Senators to success in their playoff push.
title: “Addicted to those big game feelings”: Brady Tkachuk reveals 4 Nations impact on his mindset for NHL playoffs
'Can't go anywhere': Sena workers vandalise hotel over Kunal Kamra's jibe at Shinde
Red out, blue-white in: CPM social media DP changes hue

description: The India bloc in Hindi-speaking states appears divided over the central government's proposed delimitation exercise. While Samajwadi Party chief Akhilesh Yadav supports Tamil Nadu's stance, RJD in Bihar supports the exercise, and BSP remains non-committal. JMM aligns with the Tamil Nadu CM, expressing concerns over population-based delimitation.
title: With Tamil Nadu people over delimitation, says Akhilesh; RJD backs exercise
'India has potential to play global role in nuclear technology market'
